---
title: "File upload"
lead: Lightweight, beautiful drag’n’drop file uploader.
forms-ui: true
categories: Advanced Form Elements

css_vendors:
- dropzone/dist/min/dropzone.min

js_vendors:
- dropzone/dist/dropzone

css_vendors_extended:
- dropzone
---

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            {{#card}}
                {{{card_header 'Dropzone'}}}
                {{#card_body}}
                    <p>DropzoneJS is an open source library that provides drag'n'drop file uploads with image previews. </p>
                    <!-- Dropzone -->
                    <form action="/file-upload" class="dropzone" data-plugin="dropzone">
                        <div class="dz-message">
                            <span>Drop files here or click to upload</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fallback">
                            <input name="file" type="file" multiple/>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <!-- /Dropzone -->
                    <small class="text-muted pt-2">(This is just a demo dropzone. Selected files are <strong>not</strong> actually uploaded.)</small>
                {{/card_body}}
            {{/card}}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>